title: Phillies Fans Are Raucous, but They Didn’t Move a Seismograph
description: A viral tweet shared by thousands made it look like home runs by Bryce Harper and Alec Bohm had registered as seismic events.
dc:creator: Benjamin Hoffman
media:description: Phillies fans were extremely excited by Bryce Harper’s two-run homer in Game 3 of the World Series on Tuesday. Not “caused an earthquake” excited, but excited.
